    "dag_id": "RTL_RET_STUCK",
    "incident_name": "Finance bank-statement reconciliation sensor hangs",
    "category": "Stuck/Hung Job",
    "severity": "Sev-2 (High)",
    "description": "Stuck/Hung Job incident on the Returns pipeline (RTL_RET_STUCK): finance bank-statement reconciliation sensor hangs.",
    "symptoms": "A FileSensor waiting for the daily bank statement file on SFTP has been poking for 16 hours past its usual 2-hour arrival window.",
    "root_cause": "The bank's SFTP server rotated its host key without notice; the sensor's underlying paramiko client silently retries the handshake without ever raising a clear error or respecting the sensor's timeout parameter due to a library-level bug.",
    "business_impact": "Daily cash-position reconciliation blocked; treasury team operates without a reconciled cash view for the day.",
    "resolution": "Manually restart the task after updating the known_hosts entry; upgrade the SFTP hook library and enforce sensor-level timeout at the Airflow scheduler layer, not just the library layer."
  },
